---
import ToolShell from '../../components/ToolShell.astro';
import ToolResultActions from '../../components/ToolResultActions.astro';
---
<ToolShell title="Paid media waste estimator" metaTitle="Free Google & Meta Ads Waste Estimator" eyebrow="Efficiency diagnostic" description="Estimate how much paid-media spend needs investigation based on tracking, query control, feed health, creative learning and landing-page evidence.">
  <div slot="hero-card" class="waste-hero"><span>Diagnostic, not an audit</span><strong>Find the part of spend that needs evidence.</strong><p>The result is an investigation range. It does not claim that every pound can be recovered.</p></div>
  <div slot="tool" class="tool-card"><div class="waste-intro"><span>Six inputs</span><h2>Estimate the investigation range</h2><p>Answer conservatively. “Unknown” is itself a useful risk signal.</p></div><form id="waste-estimator" class="form-stack">
    <div class="form-grid"><div class="field"><label for="media-spend">Monthly paid-media spend</label><div class="input-prefix"><span>£</span><input id="media-spend" name="spend" type="number" min="1" value="20000" required /></div></div><div class="field"><label for="media-revenue">Monthly attributed revenue / value</label><div class="input-prefix"><span>£</span><input id="media-revenue" name="revenue" type="number" min="0" value="60000" required /></div></div></div>
    <div class="form-grid"><div class="field"><label for="tracking-confidence">Tracking confidence</label><select id="tracking-confidence" name="tracking" required><option value="0">Recently validated end-to-end</option><option value="5">Some known gaps or uncertainty</option><option value="10">Not recently tested / unknown</option></select></div><div class="field"><label for="conversion-quality">Conversion priorities</label><select id="conversion-quality" name="conversions" required><option value="0">Primary actions are clean and value-based</option><option value="4">Some duplicate or secondary actions</option><option value="8">All actions appear equal / unknown</option></select></div></div>
    <div class="form-grid"><div class="field"><label for="query-control">Search-term / placement control</label><select id="query-control" name="queries" required><option value="0">Reviewed weekly with exclusions</option><option value="3">Reviewed monthly</option><option value="7">Rarely reviewed / unknown</option><option value="2">Not applicable to current channels</option></select></div><div class="field"><label for="feed-health">Product feed / catalogue health</label><select id="feed-health" name="feed" required><option value="0">Actively segmented and optimised</option><option value="3">Valid but minimally optimised</option><option value="7">Diagnostics or structure need work</option><option value="2">Not applicable</option></select></div></div>
    <div class="form-grid"><div class="field"><label for="creative-learning">Creative learning system</label><select id="creative-learning" name="creative" required><option value="0">Regular structured tests and learnings</option><option value="3">New creative without a clear test plan</option><option value="7">Low volume or long periods unchanged</option><option value="2">Not applicable</option></select></div><div class="field"><label for="landing-evidence">Landing-page evidence</label><select id="landing-evidence" name="landing" required><option value="0">Research and experiments inform changes</option><option value="3">Occasional improvements</option><option value="7">No recent review / unknown</option></select></div></div>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Estimate spend to investigate</button>
  </form><div class="result-panel" id="waste-results" aria-live="polite"><div class="waste-result-head"><div><span>Investigation range</span><h2 id="risk-label">—</h2></div><strong id="risk-score">—</strong></div><div class="waste-number"><small>Monthly spend that deserves closer review</small><strong id="monthly-range">—</strong><span id="annual-range">— annually</span></div><div class="result-grid"><div class="result-item"><strong id="reported-roas">—</strong><span>Current attributed ROAS</span></div><div class="result-item"><strong id="range-percent">—</strong><span>Modelled investigation range</span></div></div><div class="waste-priorities"><h3>Start the audit here</h3><ol id="waste-priorities"></ol></div><div class="waste-action"><div><strong>This amount is not automatically “waste”.</strong><p>It is the value of spend exposed to weak controls or evidence and worth investigating first.</p></div><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-arrow">Request an account review</a></div><ToolResultActions toolName="paid_media_waste_estimator" resultId="waste-results" resultTitle="Paid media investigation result" /><p class="disclaimer">Heuristic estimate only. The range is generated from your answers and is not a prediction of recoverable savings or future performance.</p></div></div>
  <h2>What counts as waste?</h2><p>Waste is not simply a campaign below an arbitrary ROAS benchmark. It can include spend optimising towards the wrong event, queries with no commercial relevance, duplicate conversions, product groups that cannot support the target or traffic sent into a weak landing experience.</p>
  <h2>Why “unknown” receives a higher risk score</h2><p>When tracking or control has not been validated, the business cannot distinguish a performance problem from a measurement problem. The first useful action is verification, not immediate budget cuts.</p>
  <h2>Audit in commercial order</h2><ol><li>Confirm conversion and revenue signals.</li><li>Compare targets with actual margin and new-customer value.</li><li>Inspect where the spend went: queries, placements, products and audiences.</li><li>Review the offer and landing journey receiving that traffic.</li><li>Change budget only after the evidence supports it.</li></ol>
</ToolShell>
<script>
  const wasteForm=document.getElementById('waste-estimator');
  const wasteMoney=new Intl.NumberFormat('en-GB',{style:'currency',currency:'GBP',maximumFractionDigits:0});
  wasteForm?.addEventListener('submit',event=>{event.preventDefault();const data=new FormData(wasteForm);const spend=Number(data.get('spend')),revenue=Number(data.get('revenue'));const factors=['tracking','conversions','queries','feed','creative','landing'];const scores=Object.fromEntries(factors.map(key=>[key,Number(data.get(key))]));const points=Object.values(scores).reduce((sum,value)=>sum+value,0);const lowRate=Math.min(.3,.03+points/180),highRate=Math.min(.4,.07+points/120);const low=spend*lowRate,high=spend*highRate;const labels={tracking:'Validate purchase, value, consent and deduplication end-to-end.',conversions:'Separate primary commercial conversions from diagnostic actions.',queries:'Review search terms, placements and exclusion controls.',feed:'Segment and optimise the product feed by commercial value.',creative:'Create a structured creative hypothesis and learning log.',landing:'Review landing-page friction before buying more traffic.'};const priorities=Object.entries(scores).sort((a,b)=>b[1]-a[1]).filter(([,value])=>value>0).slice(0,3).map(([key])=>labels[key]);const riskLabel=points<=8?'Controls appear relatively strong':points<=22?'Several areas need validation':'High uncertainty across the media system';const displayedPriorities=priorities.length?priorities:['Maintain the current controls and validate them on a regular cadence.'];document.getElementById('risk-label').textContent=riskLabel;document.getElementById('risk-score').textContent=`${Math.round(points/46*100)}/100`;document.getElementById('monthly-range').textContent=`${wasteMoney.format(low)}–${wasteMoney.format(high)}`;document.getElementById('annual-range').textContent=`${wasteMoney.format(low*12)}–${wasteMoney.format(high*12)} annually`;document.getElementById('reported-roas').textContent=spend>0?`${(revenue/spend).toFixed(2)}×`:'—';document.getElementById('range-percent').textContent=`${Math.round(lowRate*100)}–${Math.round(highRate*100)}%`;document.getElementById('waste-priorities').innerHTML=displayedPriorities.map(item=>`<li>${item}</li>`).join('');const results=document.getElementById('waste-results');results.dataset.resultSummary=['Spires Digital — paid media investigation result',`Outcome: ${riskLabel}`,`Control-risk score: ${Math.round(points/46*100)}/100`,`Monthly spend to investigate: ${wasteMoney.format(low)}–${wasteMoney.format(high)}`,`Modelled range: ${Math.round(lowRate*100)}–${Math.round(highRate*100)}%`,`Current attributed ROAS: ${spend>0?`${(revenue/spend).toFixed(2)}×`:'Not available'}`,'Start the audit here:',...displayedPriorities.map((item,index)=>`${index+1}. ${item}`),'This range is not automatically waste or a prediction of recoverable savings.'].join('\n');results.classList.add('active');results.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',block:'start'});window.trackSpiresEvent?.('tool_complete',{tool_name:'paid_media_waste_estimator',result_type:points<=8?'low':points<=22?'medium':'high'});});
</script>
<style>.waste-hero>span,.waste-intro>span{color:#91eadb;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase}.waste-hero strong{display:block;margin:.8rem 0;color:white;font-size:1.4rem}.waste-hero p{color:#cbd2df;font-size:.78rem}.waste-intro{margin-bottom:1.5rem}.waste-intro>span{color:var(--violet-dark)}.waste-intro h2{margin:.3rem 0}.waste-intro p{color:var(--slate)}.input-prefix{display:flex;align-items:center;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #cfd5df;border-radius:9px;background:white}.input-prefix span{padding:0 .7rem;color:var(--slate);font-weight:700}.input-prefix input{border:0!important;border-radius:0!important;outline:0!important}.result-panel{background:#fff8eb;border-color:#f0d8aa}.waste-result-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;align-items:center}.waste-result-head span{color:#986413;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase}.waste-result-head h2{margin-top:.3rem;font-size:1.5rem}.waste-result-head>strong{color:#986413;font-size:1.6rem}.waste-number{margin:1rem 0;padding:1.2rem;border-radius:10px;background:var(--ink)}.waste-number small,.waste-number strong,.waste-number span{display:block}.waste-number small{color:#aab4c5}.waste-number strong{margin:.25rem 0;color:white;font-size:2.3rem;letter-spacing:-.05em}.waste-number span{color:#91eadb;font-size:.72rem}.waste-priorities{padding:1rem;border-radius:10px;background:white}.waste-priorities h3{font-size:1rem}.waste-priorities ol{display:grid;gap:.45rem;margin-top:.7rem;padding-left:1.2rem;color:var(--slate);font-size:.78rem}.waste-action{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;align-items:center;margin-top:1rem;padding:1rem;border-radius:10px;background:white}.waste-action strong{color:var(--ink)}.waste-action p{color:var(--slate);font-size:.7rem}.waste-action .btn{flex:0 0 auto}.disclaimer{margin-top:1rem}@media(max-width:650px){.waste-action{align-items:stretch;flex-direction:column}}</style>
